name: ChartBoxwhiskerOptions
description: Represents the properties for Box & Whisker chart.

properties.name: showInnerPoints
properties.description: Returns or sets if inner points showed in a Box & whisker chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: showOutlierPoints
properties.description: Returns or sets if outlier points showed in a Box & whisker chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: showMeanMarker
properties.description: Returns or sets if mean marker showed in a Box & whisker chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: showMeanLine
properties.description: Returns or sets if mean line showed in a Box & whisker chart. ReadWrite.

properties.name: quartileCalculation
properties.description: Returns or sets quartile calculation type of a Box & whisker chart. ReadWrite.
